oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hank Williams New Years Eve Appearance Cancellation Apology
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various speeches of Hank Williams apologizing for being unable to perform for Baltimore and Washington shows on New Years Eve.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Hank Williams
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: (00:00) Hank Williams speaking about the Baltimore show and his inability to perform due to operation -- (03:21) Hank Williams begins to speak about Jimmy Davis and his inability to perform in Baltimore before being abruptly cut-off -- (03:57) Hank Williams speaking about his show in Washington and his inability to perform due to operation
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Williams, Hank, 1923-1953;
